# Project Structure - shadcn-isp-client

Next.js 16+ App Router project using shadcn/ui, TypeScript, and TailwindCSS.

## Root Structure

```
├── app/                 # Next.js App Router pages and API routes
├── auth/                # NextAuth configuration
├── components/          # React components
├── context/             # React context providers
├── data/                # Static JSON data files
├── hooks/               # Custom React hooks
├── lib/                 # Utility functions and API helpers
├── public/              # Static assets
├── types/               # TypeScript type definitions
```

## Key Directories

### `/app` - Pages & Routes
- `(dashboard)/` - Dashboard route group with layouts
  - `clients/` - Client management pages
  - `users/` - User management pages
  - `setting/` - Settings pages (dashboard, general, table, themes)
  - `tables/` - Data table pages
- `api/` - API routes (auth, theme)
- `login/` - Authentication page

### `/components` - UI Components
- `ui/` - shadcn/ui base components (button, input, dialog, etc.)
- `form/` - Form field components (input-field, checkbox, radio, switch, textarea)
- `form-wrapper/` - Form builder and wrapper utilities
- `data-table/` - Data table with pagination, filtering, sorting
- `table/` - Simplified table components
- `clients/` - Client-specific components and schemas
- `users/` - User-specific components and schemas
- `settings/` - Settings page components
- `customizer/` - Theme customizer components
- `schema/` - Zod validation schemas

### `/context` - Providers
- `AuthProvider.tsx` - Authentication context
- `SettingsProvider.tsx` - App settings context
- `theme-provider.tsx` - Theme context (light/dark)
- `theme-data-provider.tsx` - Theme data context
- `tanstack-provider.tsx` - TanStack Query provider
- `I18nProvider.tsx` - Internationalization

### `/lib` - Utilities
- `api/api.ts` - API client functions
- `auth/auth-token.ts` - Token management
- `helper/helper.ts` - General helpers
- `utils/fetch.ts` - Fetch utilities
- `utils.ts` - cn() and common utilities

### `/hooks` - Custom Hooks
- `use-mobile.tsx` - Mobile detection
- `use-pagination.ts` - Pagination logic
- `use-toast.ts` - Toast notifications

## Important Files

- `middleware.ts` - Next.js middleware for auth protection
- `tailwind.config.ts` - TailwindCSS configuration
- `components.json` - shadcn/ui configuration
- `next.config.ts` - Next.js configuration
- `auth/auth.ts` & `auth/auth.config.ts` - NextAuth setup

## Conventions

- Feature components go in `/components/{feature}/`
- Zod schemas paired with forms: `*-zod-schema.ts`, `*-form-schema.ts`
- Column definitions for tables: `*-column.tsx`
- Form components: `*-form.tsx`
- Table components: `*-table.tsx`
